<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA614_06_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema614_06.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema614_06_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y">어항에 있는 물고기 25마리 중 구피가 14마리입니다. 구피 수는 전체 물고기 수의 몇 ％인지 두 가지 방법으로 나타내어 봅시다.​</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <div class="input_area">
          <article class="page page_1">
            <h3 lang="y">백분율로 나타내는 방법을 알아보세요.</h3>

            <div class="question_box">
              <div class="col col1">
                <div class="tit">
                  <span class="label"><i>방법1</i></span>
                  <span class="tit_txt">기준량을 100으로 할 때의 비율로 바꾸어 나타내기​</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ex_box">
                  <span class="n1">0</span>
                  <span class="n2">14</span>
                  <span class="n3">25 (마리)</span>
                  <span class="n4">0</span>
                  <span class="n5">
                    <div class="input_wrap answer1" data-hint-position="right">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="56"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span class="n6">100 (마리)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ex_box2">
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span class="input_wrap answer2" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field data-answer-single="14"></math-field>
                    </span>
                    <span class="f32b">25</span>
                  </span>
                  <span class="f32b">=</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span class="input_wrap answer3" data-hint-position="up">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="56"></math-field>
                    </span>
                    <span class="f32b">100</span>
                  </span>
                  <span class="f32b">=</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer4">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="56"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span class="f32b">％</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col col2">
                <div class="tit">
                  <span class="label"><i>방법2</i></span>
                  <span class="tit_txt">비율에 100을 곱해서 나온 값에 ％를 붙여 나타내기​</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ex_box">
                  <span class="n1">비율</span>
                  <span class="n2">0</span>
                  <span class="n3">
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>14</span>
                      <span>25</span>
                    </span>
                    <span class="f32b">=</span>
                    <span>0.56</span>
                  </span>
                  <span class="n4">1</span>
                  <span class="n5">백분율</span>
                  <span class="n6">0</span>
                  <div class="n7">
                    <div class="input_wrap answer1" data-hint-position="right">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="56"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="n8 f32b">100 ％</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ex_box2">
                  <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap answer2">
                    <math-field data-answer-single="(14)/(25)"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span class="f32b times">&times;</span>
                  <span class="f32b">100</span>
                  <span class="f32b">=</span>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer3 arr">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="56"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <div class="input_wrap answer4">
                    <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="56"></math-field>
                  </div>
                  <span class="f32b">％</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="page page_2">
            <h3 lang="y"><img src=".././../common_contents/common/img/title_mid_9.svg" alt="방법1" />과 <img src=".././../common_contents/common/img/title_mid_10.svg" alt="방법2" />를 비교하여 이야기해 보세요.</h3>

            <div class="question_box justify_center">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                <div class="example_box">
                  <p>
                    방법 1은 기준량을 100으로 할 때의 비율로 바꾸어 나타냈고,<br />
                    방법 2는 비율에 100을 곱해서 나온 값에 ％를 붙여 나타냈습니다.​
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">제출</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
